// Copy to Local.xcconfig (gitignored) to customize your local Debug build.
//
//   cp Local.xcconfig.example Local.xcconfig
//
// Setting DEVELOPMENT_TEAM makes the Debug build get signed with your Apple
// Development cert (Automatic signing) instead of the default ad-hoc signature.
// Benefit: macOS TCC (Files & Folders, Full Disk Access, etc.) identifies your
// build by its stable designated requirement, so granted permissions survive
// rebuilds — no more "allow mux0 to access Documents" popups every `xcodebuild`.
//
// Where to find your Team ID: Xcode → Settings → Accounts → pick your Apple ID
// → Team column (10-char alphanumeric).
//
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = XXXXXXXXXX
